Package cmpt355.project

Class Compiler

java.lang.Object
cmpt355.project.Compiler
public class Compiler
extends Object
A class that compiles Java code into JVM assembly. As the project is incomplete, currently it can only build an AST (Abstract Syntax Tree) and then typecheck it.

      public static void main​(String... args)
